     F******************************************** ALDR80 **
     FALDPP30 IP  E                    DISK
     FALDWP80 O   E                    DISK
     F            ALDPP301                          KRENAMEALDWP801
     FALDWP81 O   E                    DISK
     F            ALDPP301                          KRENAMEALDWP811
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A3SHZ
     I                                        1   40A3SYYY
     I                                        5   60A3SYMM
     I                                        7   80A3SYDD
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PHIZK   8
     C                     PARM           PRECD   7
     C                     PARM           PKENS   7
     C                     MOVE PHIZK     WHIZK   80
      *
